{"data":[{"date":"09:33 23/07","title":"Klopp khen ng\u1ee3i sao Dortmund sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/klopp-khen-ngoi-sao-dortmund-sau-tran-thua-cua-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKarius gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 sai l\u1ea7m tai h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Karius tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u l\u00e0 \u201cLord\u201d, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1ed7i khi c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ecu m\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u201cKarius nh\u1eadp\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3. Sau tr\u1eadn, Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i post tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram nh\u01b0 sau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m vui ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean n\u1ed7i \u0111au kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho h\u1ecd. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1eebng x\u1ea5u t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Thu-mon-Loris-Karius-dap-tra-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Iker Casillas c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Loris Karius. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Porto chia s\u1ebb: \u201cNh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o Karius bao gi\u1edd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t? C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Karius?\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cH\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00ean! C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i, nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta v\u1eady\u201d \u2013 c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, d\u00f9 Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u2013 khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a khi anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\">Klopp: Karius b\u1ecb sang ch\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nKlopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1536","checkdouble":"191819"},{"date":"10:45 23/07","title":"Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/mourinho-thua-nhan-mukhong-the-mua-them-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u00ean TTCN, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 M.U kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, khi th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt. Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i th\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn Los Angeles, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 5 tr\u1eadn, kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0 quay l\u1ea1i Manchester. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf Los Angeles nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111ang \u1edf San Jose. Trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn MU kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn MU kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Kha-nang-lon-MU-khong-mua-them-tan-binh-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn M.U kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa man trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, M.U c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o Alexis Sanchez h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c xin visa. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ri\u00eang v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng theo quan s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Alexis ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Lee Grant. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 M.U kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial-172-191818.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial-172-191818.html\">MU l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c m\u00f9a h\u00e8...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my-172-191817.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/Kha-nang-lon-MU-khong-mua-them-tan-binh-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my-172-191817.html\">Mourinho b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9?</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1535","checkdouble":"191821"},{"date":"11:30 23/07","title":"Karius: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/karius-lan-dau-tien-phan-ung-ve-nhung-chi-trich.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKarius gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 sai l\u1ea7m tai h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Karius tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u l\u00e0 \u201cLord\u201d, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1ed7i khi c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ecu m\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u201cKarius nh\u1eadp\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3. Sau tr\u1eadn, Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i post tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram nh\u01b0 sau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m vui ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean n\u1ed7i \u0111au kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho h\u1ecd. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1eebng x\u1ea5u t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Thu-mon-Loris-Karius-dap-tra-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Iker Casillas c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Loris Karius. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Porto chia s\u1ebb: \u201cNh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o Karius bao gi\u1edd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t? C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Karius?\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cH\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00ean! C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i, nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta v\u1eady\u201d \u2013 c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, d\u00f9 Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u2013 khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a khi anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\">Klopp: Karius b\u1ecb sang ch\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nKlopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1534","checkdouble":"191822"},{"date":"09:22 23/07","title":"V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a \"l\u00ean m\u00e2y\" sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/37644906_1127134190773741_5719358041116114944_n.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu mon Dang Van Lam\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/37644906_1127134190773741_5719358041116114944_n.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0 song nh\u1edd tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00ean sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra v\u1ec1 an to\u00e0n sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n &lsquo;bay l\u01b0\u1ee3n&rsquo; c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen d\u00e0nh cho anh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y L\u00e2m &quot;T\u00e2y&quot; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u Nga, \u00f4ng V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh&rsquo; B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;&#10;color:#222222\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1533","checkdouble":"191823"},{"date":"11:34 23/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 23/7: M.U \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ngay-hom-nay-237.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (23/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 237, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 237, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-167,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alex Sandro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Duncan Castles ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, MU \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus, trong s\u1ef1 tranh \u0111ua quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a MU ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i PSG, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro h\u00f2ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \"l\u1eadt k\u00e8o\" c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch b\u00e1n Alex Sandro, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 cao. MU \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alex Sandro. V\u00ec anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf Juventus, n\u00ean MU d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u00f3i: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i cho b\u1ea1n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a MU, PSG c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro khi \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 MU h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi Alex Sandro\".</div>\r\n<h2>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cho Real 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ee5 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng Gia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh ch\u01a1i 36 tr\u1eadn cho Real nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn l\u00e0 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Real, gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ed do t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mateo-kovacic-yeu-cau-duoc-roi-real-madrid-180-191805.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Maurizio Sarri c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua 3 ng\u00f4i sao Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fali Ramadani sang Italy \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Juventus v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Gonzalo Higuain, Daniele Rugani \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Miralem Pjanic. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Chelsea d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecfi mua Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro, Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi Miralem Pjanic c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Higuain l\u00e0 Juve v\u00e0 Chelsea ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1. V\u1edbi Rugani, Juve c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n. V\u1edbi Pjanic, Juve \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 237 MU \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 237 MU \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-237-MU-da-nhan-duoc-cai-gat-dau-cua-Alex-Sandro--hinh-anh-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Milan nh\u1eafm mua 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1n quy\u1ebft cho ph\u00e9p d\u1ef1 Europa League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00f2a \u00e1n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ec3 thao (TAS), Milan l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u00f3 tin n\u00f3i Milan \u0111ang nh\u1eafm mua \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 trong 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0 Morata (Chelsea), Benzema (Real) v\u00e0 Higuain (Juventus). Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Benzema, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin anh mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Milan. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Higuain, Juve \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i 60 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t l\u00e0 30/7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Argentina. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Morata, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Juve thay v\u00ec Milan.</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal mua l\u1ea1i Giroud sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sky Sports b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay ch\u00ednh Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Giroud sang Chelsea, n\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea s\u1eafp mua trung phong Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus, Giroud c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal n\u1ebfu \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca, v\u1ec1 Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trang web Goal.com cho bi\u1ebft trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t xong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Everton v\u00e0 gi\u1edd hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd Barcelona \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. Mina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng sau th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup cho \u0110T Colombia v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Everton Marco Silva.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca</span><br>\r\n<span>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca. Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng anh gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona cho h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Karius s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean, Loris Karius v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u201cThe Kop\u201d v\u1eeba mua v\u1ec1 Alisson t\u1eeb AS Roma. \u201cLoris l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1532","checkdouble":"191825"},{"date":"11:49 23/07","title":"Ph\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1edbng Zola \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi Chelsea ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 HLV m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/25/huyen-thoai-chelsea-canh-giac-phong-do-cua-sat-thu-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd cho HLV Sarri, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gianfranco Zola y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nChelsea ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge loay hoay v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa Conte &ndash; Sarri \u00edt ng\u00e0y. Trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chinh chi\u1ebfn cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau. Nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eddi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea &ndash; Gianfranco Zola l\u00e0m ph\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1edbng cho \u00f4ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn, tr\u00e1nh \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c sa th\u1ea3i HLV.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn&rdquo; &ndash; Zola cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf CLB c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t, cung c\u1ea5p cho Sarri th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zola y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb Chelsea cho HLV m\u1edbi\" title=\"Sarri Zola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zola y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb Chelsea cho HLV m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Sarri, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1eefng HLV c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm. Sarri v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; Zola k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Zola y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay t\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1eefa d\u00f2ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Maurizio Sarri c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Antonio Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-gian-nan-vi-thoi-duong-ho-di-hoa-172-191620.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/Eden-Hazard-and-Thibaut-Courtois.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-gian-nan-vi-thoi-duong-ho-di-hoa-172-191620.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Gian nan v\u00ec th\u00f3i &ldquo;d\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u1ed5 di h\u1ecda&rdquo;</span><br>\r\n\u00cdt ng\u00e0y qua, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft Chelsea...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri-172-191093.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri-172-191093.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sarri quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea &ldquo;ph\u1ee5 t\u00ecnh&rdquo; Conte?</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng cho Conte \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1531","checkdouble":"191826"},{"date":"11:51 23/07","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/23/sau-vong-20-vleague-su-vo-doi-cua-ha-noi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed9t tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 v\u1edbi n\u1eeda c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a h\u00fa v\u00eda tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson, Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng khi\u1ebfn cho kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng th\u00e0nh 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/tuandeu-165-15322166038181671998768.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. S\u1ef1 tr\u1ed7i d\u1eady c\u1ee7a SLNA<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng khi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, tuy nhi\u00ean \u00edt ai ng\u1edd, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 8 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 Olaha tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1edf n\u00ean nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap SLNA s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 8 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League do CLB G\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1ed3ng T\u00e2m Long An thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2005. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y SLNA c\u00f2n \u0111ang m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH sau 20 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl-168-191757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl-168-191757.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 trong su\u1ed1t 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0. G\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t SLNA \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-3 chung cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Vinh sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL, d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" title=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura t\u1ea1m an to\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Matias Nicolas J.Gonzalez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura t\u1ea1m qua c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c. Sau hai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 leo l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. Duy tr\u00ec t\u1ed1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u1eeda tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 14 tr\u00ean BXH. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng cho HLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u V\u0169 Quang B\u1ea3o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung g\u1ea5p g\u00e1p n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00fap C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u01a1n nguy k\u1ecbch? H\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y c\u1ea7n v\u1ef1c l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 ngu\u1ed9i l\u1ea1nh sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng sau s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i V-Leauge \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH sau vong 20 V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/BXH-vong-20-V-Leauge-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Highlight Thanh H\u00f3a 2-3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></h3>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/21/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1530","checkdouble":"191828"},{"date":"07:20 23/07","title":"B\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, M.U c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/bi-clb-my-cam-hoa-mu-con-mat-tru-cot-do-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi SJ Earthquakes t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Levi trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Matteo Darmian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Valencia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. HLV Jose Mourinho lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c khi M.U ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU b\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU b\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Valencia-roi-san-do-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t Valencia do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Mourinho c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea7y lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a M.U. Sau khi v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Club America, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u00f9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c hay d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, M.U \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez m\u1edbi t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 t\u1eadp trung song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qua nhieu bai toan hoc bua cho HLV Jose Mourinho truoc mua giai moi\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00f3c b\u00faa cho HLV Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/MU-0-0-San-Jose-Earthquakes-Them-mot-tran-giao-huu-that-vong-cua-bay-Quy-do-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Mourinho nhi\u1ec1u lo l\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi Sanchez r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ph\u00fat 65, th\u1ebf c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a M.U c\u0169ng y\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111i. Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung ra n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tahith Chong, Mason Greenwood r\u1ed3i Angel Gomes&hellip; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat, M.U ch\u1ec9 tung ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd b\u1ecb SJ Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool-172-191802.html\">B\u1ecb ch\u00ea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho... Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\">MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1529","checkdouble":"191813"},{"date":"07:51 23/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 23/7: Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-237-tiet-lo-3-muc-tieu-cung-co-hang-thu-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 23/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, M.U c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. </strong>Man United ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. </strong>Manchester United \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Harry Maguire, Toby Alderweireld ho\u1eb7c Leonardo Bonucci. Nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 237 Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 237 Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/Thuong-vu-MU-mua-Leonardo-Bonucci-co-dien-bien-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bonucci l\u00e0 1 trong 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nSao Man City ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. </strong>Aymeric Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Les Bleus khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 mang v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u cho Liverpool.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Steve Nicol tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca. </strong>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca. Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng anh gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona cho h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" title=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/sao-sang-world-cup-thua-nhan-co-the-bi-da-khoi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool. </strong>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Lovren, Van Dijk r\u1ed3i Klavan, Gomez cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus.</strong> Nh\u1eefng ai tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. L\u00fd do n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juve s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p sau khi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1528","checkdouble":"191814"},{"date":"08:19 23/07","title":"T\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup, HLV Croatia t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/tao-ky-tich-o-world-cup-hlv-croatia-tu-lam-gia-ban-than.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatko Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n 5 tri\u1ec7u USD/n\u0103m.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Dalic l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Croatia</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong-465-191335.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n</span> v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Balkan l\u00e0 Luka Modric, l\u00e0 Ivan Raktitic v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00ednh HLV Zlatko Dalic.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 52 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau khi sa th\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Ante Cacic v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/tao-ky-tich-o-world-cup-hlv-croatia-tu-lam-gia-ban-than.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t Dalic v\u00f4 danh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn HLV n\u00e0y (7 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c Trung \u0110\u00f4ng) \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch t\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Dalic \u00fap m\u1edf chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i, t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng Croatia, Dalic gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB Premier League nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;C\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1eady th\u00ec con s\u1ed1 5 tri\u1ec7u USD/n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00edt \u1ecfi so v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng m\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c quan tr\u1ecdng th\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n hai n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng Ba r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.&rdquo; &ndash; Dalic b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\">B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia: \u0110\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1edbn</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Mala zemlja, veliki snovi&rdquo; &ndash; D\u00f2ng ch\u1eef ti\u1ebfng Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean xe bus ch\u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia rong ru\u1ed5i c\u1ea3 th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 qua tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. D\u1ecbch ra ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t:...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1527","checkdouble":"191815"},{"date":"08:16 23/07","title":"Mourinho b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM.U b\u1ecb SJ Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb Club America c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, Man United l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose Earthquakes. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u01b0a th\u1edbt t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Levi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 M.U d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 tung ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, \u00edt h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi SJ Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 SJ Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 SJ Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-sau-tran-MU-0-0-SJ-Earthquakes-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sanchez kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap M.U th\u1eafng SJ Earthquakes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c M.U h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Club America, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp n\u1eefa&rdquo;, Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1edbi k\u00eanh MUTV. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c nhau. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i 1, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 U23, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1ec1 ho\u1eb7c m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tai My\" title=\"Mourinho tai My\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Andreas Pereira l\u00e0 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y Mourinho. &ldquo;Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i sau m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Sanchez c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng khen.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Pereira c\u0169ng \u1ed5n, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\">MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-mu-lo-so-bi-cac-tai-nang-tre-dan-em-cuop-cho-172-191775.html\">Sao MU lo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e0n em c\u01b0\u1edbp ch\u1ed7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1526","checkdouble":"191817"},{"date":"08:49 23/07","title":"MU l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Khi Romelu Lukaku v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn trong s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Man Utd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\" target=\"_blank\">CLB M\u1ef9 San Jose Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0</span>. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u1edf IC Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 anh ra kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eb1m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, v\u1eady n\u00ean Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m giam c\u1ea7m c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Los Angeles, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n hay thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Manchester chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf San Jose v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Martial \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103m tia nghi\u00eam t\u00fac b\u1edfi Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Man Utd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng \u201cn\u1ed1i gi\u00e1o cho gi\u1eb7c\u201d trong l\u00f2ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 b\u00e1n anh cho Bayern Munich.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/23/MU-1-0-San-Jose.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1525","checkdouble":"191818"},{"date":"08:53 23/07","title":"HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 chung cu\u1ed9c nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Matias Gonzalez. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura \u0111\u00e3 b\u1edbt ph\u1ea7n lung linh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Toshiya Miura l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb. Sau pha b\u00f3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, ch\u01b0a chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>Trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mong Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c tinh th\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi anh ta\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Miura cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng x\u1ea5u x\u00ed,\u00a0\u0111\u00e1ng l\u00ean \u00e1n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>V\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i treo gi\u00f2 v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i V-League. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, HLV Miura cho hay: \u00a0\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 CLB ph\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf. Hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 6 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cK\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ho\u00e0 nh\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0 Quang Huy ho\u1eb7c Marclei Santos ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. Kesley th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00ec anh ta bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t. D\u00f9 sao \u0111i n\u1eefa, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng ngh\u0129 ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt\u201d, \u00f4ng Miura ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB TP.HCM l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 v\u1edbi 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 t\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191786.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191786.html\">TPHCM 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (KT): V\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Miura l\u1ea1i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m nguy hi\u1ec3m</span><br />\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Matias Jadue gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Toshiya Miura th\u1eafng 2-1 khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i Nuti Caf\u00e9 V-League 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1524","checkdouble":"191820"},{"date":"22:37 22/07","title":"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matip tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Cameroon \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Matip bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i theo d\u00f5i The Kop thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Lovren v\u00e0 Van Dijk t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 \u0103n \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho Lovren c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a sau. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o 6/8 t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matip s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd v\u1eady, Matip s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Ragnar Klavan cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Van Dijk. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Schalke t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 100% nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian n\u1eefa\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Matip tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. The Kop li\u00ean t\u1ee5c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Naby Keita, Fabinho, Alisson Becker c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Shaqiri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ra sao nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-ve-phat-bieu-mu-172-191769.html\">Klopp: MU m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c Liverpool, c\u00f2n Liverpool m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-nhm-liverpool-deu-muon-nghe-tin-nay-tu-klopp-172-191760.html\">100% NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nghe tin n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Klopp?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1523","checkdouble":"191801"},{"date":"23:59 22/07","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u00ea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho... Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Christian Pulisic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pulisic<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi 174 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed1n c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Alisson (66.8), Naby Keita (52.75), Fabinho (43), Shaqiri (13.5), Liverpool c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 Christian Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Christian Pulisic.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"T\u00f4i th\u00edch Pulisic, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb. Pulisic ch\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Anh ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng Pulisic \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 14 \u0111\u1ebfn 15 n\u0103m trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p n\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u1edbi Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u00e0? T\u00f4i ch\u1ecbu\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Pulisic v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Dortmund. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho MU<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Jurgen Klopp t\u1eebng ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch Manchester United ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec Paul Pogba v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Kop l\u1ea1i bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Klopp h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng m\u1eafc quai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ec7n minh cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson, Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 th\u1eeba cho Man Utd: \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u1ebft ti\u1ec7t b\u1ea1n n\u00f3i, ch\u1eb3ng ai qu\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. T\u00f4i l\u00e0m sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhanh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng hai n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\"M\u1ed9t tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u th\u1eadt l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Man Utd t\u1eebng b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Liverpool:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong-172-191761.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-nhm-liverpool-deu-muon-nghe-tin-nay-tu-klopp-172-191760.html\">100% NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nghe tin n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Klopp?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool-180-191758.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings-172-191735.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool s\u1eafp chia tay Danny Ings</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-luon-tuong-tuong-minh-se-tro-thanh-gerrard-172-191724.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Gerrard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-172-191696.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ea3nh, n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1522","checkdouble":"191802"}]}